Turai Yar'Adua and Umaru Musa Yar'Adua were married for 35 years before Umaru Musa Yar'Adua died, leaving behind his partner and 1 child.

They had a daughter named Zainab.

About

Turai Yar'Adua is a 66 year old Nigerian First Lady born on 26th July, 1957 in Katsina area, Nigeria. Her zodiac sign is Leo
